name: United 787-8 N29907 Delivery Flight from Paine Field
description:
This is the delivery flight of United's latest 787, N29907 departing Paine Field in Everett, Washington, for Denver. Fellow spotter OwnsGermany also shot a video of the same flight, check it out here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=knLkHHlsNuo I hope you enjoy, and stay tuned for many more Paine Field videos!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
